casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Jahan Satati GREEN, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157429
COA: 332835 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 24, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the December 19, 2017 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court. The motion for miscellaneous relief is DENIED.
